               also can be sensitive to the choice of reference data. In
               addition, it was found that the model performances show
               significant regional variations.},
	author = {Anav, A and Friedlingstein, P and Kidston, M and Bopp, L and Ciais, P and Cox, P and Jones, C and Jung, M and Myneni, R and Zhu, Z},
	journal = {J. Clim.},
	month = sep,
	number = 18,
	pages = {6801--6843},
